posting_body: ['Travis Heights Terrace, 2303 East Side Drive #11, Austin, TX 78704.', 'Privately individually owned Condo Residential Community.', "What we've loved about living so central and close-in Travis Heights, Soco.", 'the Neighborhood is walkable and wonderful, near Stacy & Little Stacy Park & Pool.', 'Big Heritage Trees for neighborhood shade.', 'Walking distance to excellent commercial life, live music, restaurants on South Congress Avenue.', "Continental Club, C-Boys, South Congress Hotel, Jo's Coffee, Guero's, Magnolia Cafe, Torchy's, and many more.", ' 80/100 on the Walk  Bicycle Score website.', '$2,450 for Lease.', 'Also Active in ABOR MLS for Sale @ 419,850.', 'Per TCAD the Square footage of this first floor level 2 full bedroom, 2 full bathroom quaint, quite condo is 964 sq.', 'ft.', 'It is gate protect complex, the unit comes with 2 parking space and gate clickers.', 'Dishwasher, Fridge, Electric Stove, nearby Community Washer Dryer is easily phone app operated.', 'Google Fiber Inter Service is available at this geographic location.', 'this Unit can be shown now by appointment, but the new tenant lease date is in the August 15th to September 1st', 'start date range.', 'Ownership is looking for quality, qualified long term tenants with zero pets, especially no large dogs.', 'At this time, ownership would prefer to lease, but the sale asking price is $395,000-419K', 'Listing Broker / Co - Owner', 'George Vance McGee', '<URL>', 'Broker Associate', 'show contact info']
